rows.label: qst620301_msg0001
rows.name:
It's a wonderful place, Liberalitas.
Don't you think so?

rows.label: qst620301_msg0002
rows.name:
I've read about it, but the real thing
is something else! I feel so free, and
the nature, the weather? Ahhhh...

rows.label: qst620301_msg0003
rows.name:
I came here with my girlfriend, and it
really did wonders for us.

rows.label: qst620301_msg0004
rows.name:
See, her father's just like you guys,
a real go-getter, capable as anything.

rows.label: qst620301_msg0005
rows.name:
But that puts him in such high demand,
he hardly ever finds time to meet up
with his daughter.

rows.label: qst620301_msg0006
rows.name:
I mean, what can you do, right?
But he's her only living family, and
I can tell it gets to her sometimes...

rows.label: qst107301_msg0020
rows.name: 納得

rows.label: qst620301_msg0007
rows.name:
Anyway, since you all look so capable...
I was wondering if I could talk to you
about something.

rows.label: qst620301_msg0008
rows.name:
I wanted to propose to my girlfriend.
Here, in Liberalitas. But I might need
some help... Would you mind...?

rows.label: qst620301_msg0009
rows.name:
All I need is a special precious stone,
and also safe passage to a place
with that romantic kind of mood!

rows.label: qst620301_msg0010
rows.name: Simple, right?

rows.label: qst107301_msg0025
rows.name: 受注2

rows.label: qst620301_msg0011
rows.name: Oh, thanks so much!

rows.label: qst620301_msg0012
rows.name:
Let's deal with the rock first, then.
It's for the engagement ring, you see.

rows.label: qst620301_msg0013
rows.name:
My buddy Mogumogu told me about these
brilliant white gems called Posystones.

rows.label: qst620301_msg0014
rows.name:
Apparently they only come from
this one specific cave in Luxuria.

rows.label: qst620301_msg0015
rows.name:
What was the name again...? Uhh...
Pippito's Haunt, or something?

rows.label: qst620301_msg0016
rows.name:
My original plan was to go back to
Invidia, work hard and save up, then
beg Mogumogu to sell me one, but...

rows.label: qst620301_msg0017
rows.name:
I don't think there'll be a better time
to pop the question than right now!

rows.label: qst620301_msg0018
rows.name:
So anyway, it's a bit far, but that's not
going to stop a go-getter like you, now,
is it? Think you could help me out?

rows.label: qst107301_msg0034
rows.name: 了解

rows.label: qst620301_msg0019
rows.name:
I'm at a turning point in my life, me.
But don't worry, I won't be stingy with
the reward, either!

rows.label: qst620301_msg0020
rows.name: Go get 'em!
